<script nonce="GbUqA8QEIprMC8+h/1POhA==" type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"http://schema.org/","@type":"Dataset","name":"What's Trending (Google India)","description":"**About This Dataset:**
This dataset offers insights into the trending topics in India over a specific timeframe. It combines data on search queries and article engagement to provide a comprehensive overview of the digital discourse within the country.


**Contents:**
- Search Date: The date range for each dataset entry.
- Search Query ID: Unique identifier for each search query.
- Search Query: Keywords or phrases used in the search.
- Search Traffic: Traffic volume related to each search query.
- Related Query: Associated queries or related topics.
- Article Title: Title of the related article.
- Article Source: Source of the article.
- Article Snippet: Summary or snippet of the article content.
- Article Link: URL link to the full article.
